---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About – CraveSmart" 
  description="Learn more about CraveSmart and our mission."
>
  <section class="bg-white text-gray-900 py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 max-w-5xl">
      <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-heading font-bold mb-8 text-center">
        About CraveSmart
      </h1>

      <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-12">
        <img 
          src="/public/placeholders/image.png" 
          alt="Micci, creator of CraveSmart" 
          class="w-full max-w-sm rounded-full shadow-xl object-cover"
        />
        <div class="flex-1 space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-700">
          <p>
            Hi, I'm Isabella, the creator of CraveSmart. I started this site because I love food, but I also care about how it fits into my life and goals.
          </p>
          <p>
            CraveSmart is all about proven viral recipes that taste incredible and support smart macros; indulgence that behaves, no guilt, no nonsense.
          </p>
          <p>
            Whether it's breakfast that fuels your day, dinner that satisfies the family, or desserts that don't derail you, everything here has been curated for real results and real enjoyment.
          </p>
          <p class="font-medium text-tiffany">
            Follow along, cook with me, and let's make cravings work for us.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>